<h2 id="intro">1. Introduction</h2>
<p>I am Maryam Yaseen, a Computer Science student at COMSATS University Islamabad (expected 2027) with a strong passion for full stack web development. I specialize in the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) and have built several production-grade applications featuring secure authentication, real-time communication, AI integration, and responsive design.</p>
<p>With a GPA of 3.97/4.00 and hands-on experience across three internships, I am seeking a Junior Full Stack Developer role where I can apply my technical expertise to build impactful, scalable solutions.</p>
<p>This report documents my projects, technical skills, professional experience, and the implementation details of my portfolio website.</p>

