<h2 id="code">4. Code Implementation</h2>
<p>The personal portfolio website was built using HTML5, CSS3, and vanilla JavaScript. Below are key implementation details:</p>

<h3>4.1 Portfolio Structure (HTML)</h3>
<p>The HTML is organized into semantic sections: navigation bar, hero section, about, education, skills, projects, experience timeline, achievements, and contact form.</p>
<pre>&lt;!-- Navigation with mobile hamburger toggle --&gt;
&lt;nav id="navbar"&gt;
